# Official submission data snapshots are intentionally commit candidates.
# Keep data_1/, data_2/, and data_3/ visible to Git.

# Local experiment workspace: personal markdown logs, figures, model binaries,
# and small interim score tables are absorbed into lab/*.ipynb instead.
/laboratory/

# Generated runtime artifacts
/models/
/outputs/
/reports/figures/

# Legacy notebook workspace is not the official submission surface.
# The curated, runnable notebooks live under lab/.
/notebooks/

# Keep only the final report from Report/.
/Report/*
!/Report/Submission/
!/Report/Submission/Team2_report.md

